  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 02/13/2018 CT 12:07pm CT (18:07 UTC)</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-PurchaseOrderItemList\">Purchase Order Item List</h2><p>We have condensed the purchase order item list to fit better on smaller screens. Specifically, we removed the SKU and UPC columns and added them as\u00a0sub-lines\u00a0in\u00a0the catalog item column.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-TicketItemDefaultQty\">Ticket Item Default Qty</h2><p>Inventoried items now always get a default qty of 1 when they are added to a ticket.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-Qsite\">Qsite</h2><p>By popular demand, the staff member's last name has been removed from\u00a0ticket comments.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-SalesReferralSummaryReportDownload\">Sales Referral Summary Report\u00a0Download</h2><p>We added a new\u00a0excel download for the Sales Referral Summary.</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-AnnouncementDeleting\">Announcement Deleting</h2><p>We fixed an issue that would prevent deleting announcements</p><h2 id=\"id-1.13.11-InventoryLockforBackorderedItems\">Inventory Lock for Backordered Items</h2><p>Inventory locks are now pro-actively released on ticket save so that the inventory items are editable afterwards (when in a non-consumed status).</p>",
      "representation": "export_view",
